OL,3,CSecond job rule change set to see
OL,4,CLabour mayor banned from re-election
OL,6,FDan Norris is expected to face a ban
OL,7,Fon running for re-election as the West
OL,8,Fof England's Metro Mayor as part of a
OL,9,Fcrackdown on MPs having second jobs,
OL,10,FITV News understands.
OL,12,FMr Norris has been a regional mayor
OL,13,Fsince May 2021 and was recently
OL,14,Felected as the MP for North East
OL,15,FSomerset and Hanham, unseating the
OL,16,FConservative Jacob Rees-Mogg.
