OL,3,CSecond job rule change set to see
OL,4,CLabour mayor banned from re-election
OL,6,FBut under changes to Labour Party
OL,7,Frules, Mr Norris looks set to be
OL,8,Fblocked from running for a second term
OL,9,Fwhen the mayoral election takes place
OL,10,Fin May next year.
OL,12,FThe Labour Party says it is "committed
OL,13,Fto MPs focusing on being MPs" and the
OL,14,Fexpected rule change "is about the
OL,15,Fprinciple of second jobbing bringing
OL,16,Fmayors into line with leaders and
OL,17,Fcouncillors in the Labour Party rule
OL,18,Fbook."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
