OL,3,CSecond job rule change set to see
OL,4,CLabour mayor banned from re-election
OL,6,FIt's understood that the process to
OL,7,Fselect a new Labour candidate for next
OL,8,Fyear's West of England Combined
OL,9,FAuthority (WECA) election will begin
OL,10,Fin a few weeks' time.
OL,12,FA number of newly elected Labour MPs
OL,13,Fin the South West have recently had to
OL,14,Fstand down as local councillors as a
OL,15,Fresult of the Labour rulebook.
OL,17,FJayne Kirkham, Labour MP for Truro and
OL,18,FFalmouth, and Will Stone, Labour MP
OL,19,Ffor Swindon North, have both had to
OL,20,Frelinquish council roles to be full-
OL,21,Ftime members of Parliament.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
