OL,3,CSecond job rule change set to see
OL,4,CLabour mayor banned from re-election
OL,6,FMr Norris, who beat Jacob Rees-Mogg
OL,7,Fwith a majority of more than 5,000,
OL,8,Fhas spoken of his determination to
OL,9,Fcontinue in his role as WECA Mayor and
OL,10,Fas a newly elected MP.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV West Country in July,
OL,13,FMr Norris said he hadn't yet made a
OL,14,Fdecision on whether to stand down
OL,15,Fahead of the 2025 election, but
OL,16,Finsisted there was "precedent in
OL,17,Fpolitics" for MPs to do two jobs.
